arts.ttl: Coventry City vs Norwich City: EFL Championship Preview, Gameweek 5, 2025/26
arts.sum: After a two-week pause for the international break, Coventry City welcome Norwich City to the West Midlands seeking to extend their unbeaten run to the new Sky Bet Championship season to five games. Indeed, the first six competitive games of the new era in Norfolk have, bizarrely, been marked by three home losses and three away wins, and the Canaries even boast a near-perfect record at the Coventry Building Society Arena since relegation from the Premier League three years ago.
